00:03:44.230 --> 00:03:46.690
You're the only white guy
in your friend circle?

00:03:46.690 --> 00:03:47.590
I love that.

00:03:47.590 --> 00:03:49.570
Welcome to my world, now
you see how it feels,

00:03:49.570 --> 00:03:50.760
you're the minority.

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:52.960
And it gives him such an
interesting perspective

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:55.690
because in our show we
have this group of friends

00:03:55.690 --> 00:03:58.000
and they all bring their
own preconceived notions,

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:00.660
and perceptions, and upbringings
to the various topics

00:04:00.660 --> 00:04:04.000
that we discuss on the show,
and we see it all play out.

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:06.250
The title, "Truth Be Told,"
is really appropriate

00:04:06.250 --> 00:04:10.280
because in real life when
you interact-- and of course,

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:12.770
this is Google,
so you guys know--

00:04:12.770 --> 00:04:14.510
everybody now is connected.

00:04:14.510 --> 00:04:18.230
And we're connected in ways
that we weren't 10 years ago.

00:04:18.230 --> 00:04:19.860
And so you're
interacting with people

00:04:19.860 --> 00:04:21.740
that are completely
outside your particular

00:04:21.740 --> 00:04:24.745
demographic-- I don't care
if it's like people that

00:04:24.745 --> 00:04:26.637
live around you, look
like you, worship

00:04:26.637 --> 00:04:28.220
or believe in the
things you believe--

00:04:28.220 --> 00:04:30.380
like you're talking to
everybody on any given

00:04:30.380 --> 00:04:33.170
day through social media
and various networks.

00:04:33.170 --> 00:04:37.420
So it means that when you
are on those social networks

00:04:37.420 --> 00:04:38.860
oftentimes you're
brutally honest.

00:04:38.860 --> 00:04:41.880
And when somebody says,
OK, truth be told,

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:43.680
you know you just
prepare yourself

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:45.240
because whatever
comes next is going

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:46.770
to brutally honest, is
not going to be filtered,

00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.850
and that's how we
interact with real people.

00:04:48.850 --> 00:04:50.808
And so that's an appropriate
title for our show

00:04:50.808 --> 00:04:53.325
because this is a group of
four actual real friends

00:04:53.325 --> 00:04:55.970
who organically
talk about things

00:04:55.970 --> 00:04:59.075
in an unfiltered kind of way,
the way that real people do.

00:04:59.075 --> 00:05:00.950
MARJAI ROBERTS: Yeah,
