00:10:47.677 --> 00:10:50.830
makes the show a lot more
accessible when you can talk

00:10:50.830 --> 00:10:53.620
about these uncomfortable
topics in a way that

00:10:53.620 --> 00:10:55.414
brings some humor into it.

00:10:55.414 --> 00:10:56.830
And it makes just
more comfortable

00:10:56.830 --> 00:11:00.710
in starting the dialogue, so
