00:11:00.710 --> 00:11:06.140
So Tone Bell, he is a stand-up
comedian in real life, also

00:11:06.140 --> 00:11:11.280
an actor, so was that part of
his character Russell's role

00:11:11.280 --> 00:11:14.029
