00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:18.690
He likes to say that,
out of this foursome,

00:15:18.690 --> 00:15:22.700
the fifth character on the
show is Mitch's white guilt.

00:15:22.700 --> 00:15:27.270
And that is very appropriate
for our creator, DJ Nash,

00:15:27.270 --> 00:15:32.620
because he is-- in a great, fun,
and lovable way-- somebody that

00:15:32.620 --> 00:15:35.715
always wants to make sure that
he's not part of the problem

00:15:35.715 --> 00:15:37.090
and that he's
doing everything he

00:15:37.090 --> 00:15:39.790
can be a part of the solution,
whatever that may be.

00:15:39.790 --> 00:15:44.110
So he instills that in the
writing of our Mitch character,

00:15:44.110 --> 00:15:49.210
and it's really fun to have that
kind of guy opposite somebody

00:15:49.210 --> 00:15:52.777
